waaseyaa 0.1.0

Usage:
  command [options] [arguments]

Options:
  -h, --help            Display help for the given command. When no command is given display help for the list command
      --silent          Do not output any message
  -q, --quiet           Only errors are displayed. All other output is suppressed
  -V, --version         Display this application version
      --ansi|--no-ansi  Force (or disable --no-ansi) ANSI output
  -n, --no-interaction  Do not ask any interactive question
  -v|vv|vvv, --verbose  Increase the verbosity of messages: 1 for normal output, 2 for more verbose output and 3 for debug

Available commands:
  about                  Display information about the Waaseyaa installation
  completion             Dump the shell completion script
  help                   Display help for a command
  install                Install Waaseyaa with initial configuration
  list                   List commands
  migrate                Run pending database migrations (use --dry-run to preview, --verify to audit)
  optimize               Run all optimization compilers
  serve                  Start the PHP development server
  sync-rules             Sync framework rules from Waaseyaa to this app
  telescope              List recent telescope entries
 admin
  admin:build            Build the Nuxt admin SPA for static hosting (npm run generate)
  admin:dev              Run the Nuxt admin SPA in development (npm run dev)
 audit
  audit:log              Display the entity type lifecycle audit log, or entity-write audit log with --entity-type
 cache
  cache:clear            Clear one or all cache bins
 config
  config:export          Export active configuration to the sync directory
  config:import          Import configuration from the sync directory
 db
  db:init                Initialize the database on first deploy and apply pending migrations.
 debug
  debug:context          Render deterministic debug panels for workflow, traversal, and SSR context
 entity
  entity:create          Create a new entity of a given type
  entity:list            List entities of a given type
 entity-type
  entity-type:list       List all registered entity types
 event
  event:list             List all registered events and listeners
 fixture
  fixture:generate       Generate deterministic fixture scenario JSON from topology templates
  fixture:pack:refresh   Refresh deterministic fixture-pack aggregate from scenario JSON files
  fixture:scaffold       Generate deterministic workflow + relationship fixture scenario JSON
 health
  health:check           Run all diagnostic health checks and report results
  health:report          Generate a full diagnostic report for operator review
 ingest
  ingest:dashboard       Build deterministic editorial dashboard summaries from ingest artifacts
  ingest:run             Run deterministic structured/unstructured ingestion and emit mapped content payloads
 make
  make:entity            Generate a content entity class
  make:entity-type       Generate an entity type class
  make:job               Generate a queue job class
  make:listener          Generate an event listener class
  make:migration         Generate a migration file
  make:plugin            Generate a plugin class with #[WaaseyaaPlugin] attribute
  make:policy            Generate an access policy class
  make:provider          Generate a service provider class
  make:public            Scaffold the canonical public/index.php front controller
  make:test              Generate a PHPUnit test class
 migrate
  migrate:defaults       Migrate default content type enablement for tenants
  migrate:rollback       Roll back the last batch of migrations
  migrate:status         Show the status of each migration
 northcloud
  northcloud:sync        Pull content from the NorthCloud Search API and persist entities via registered mappers
 optimize
  optimize:clear         Remove all cached optimization artifacts
  optimize:config        Compile and cache all configuration
  optimize:manifest      Compile the package discovery manifest
 perf
  perf:baseline          Generate a versioned performance baseline artifact
  perf:compare           Compare current performance measurements against a baseline artifact
 permission
  permission:list        List all registered permissions
 route
  route:list             List all registered routes
 scaffold
  scaffold:auth          Copy framework auth UI files into your app for customization
  scaffold:bundle        Generate deterministic bundle scaffold JSON
  scaffold:extension     Generate deterministic external extension SDK scaffold JSON
  scaffold:relationship  Generate deterministic relationship-type scaffold JSON
  scaffold:workflow      Generate deterministic workflow scaffold JSON
 schema
  schema:check           Detect schema drift between entity type definitions and database tables
  schema:list            List registered schemas with versions and compatibility policy
 semantic
  semantic:refresh       Run resumable semantic index refresh batches
  semantic:warm          Warm semantic embeddings for deterministic read paths
 telescope
  telescope:clear        Clear all telescope entries
  telescope:prune        Prune telescope entries older than retention period
 type
  type:disable           Disable a registered content type (does not delete it)
  type:enable            Re-enable a previously disabled content type
 user
  user:create            Create a new user account
  user:role              Add or remove a role from a user
 waaseyaa
  waaseyaa:version       Print waaseyaa/* framework provenance (path SHA, lockfile versions, drift vs golden SHA)
